Job Description
Consistently develop new customer accounts
Retain existing clientele base
Liaise and communicate with engineering consultants so as to gain acceptance from consultants on Emerson products
Deploy different strategies to win jobs in the marketplace
Expand market share in the allocated business market segment assigned to
Work in line with the sales organization's business objectives / directions to attain a common goal
Create differentiation in your selling through strategic selling of total solutions
Achieve the set target. Able to work and think in line with company's business directions
Aggressive in sales engagement and adherence to company's work ethics
Able to work in a fast paced and dynamic sales environment
Independent, proactive and possess a positive mind set
A problem solver
Possess proper and professional business ethics
Possess a never-say-die work attitude
Receptive to company's systematic work processes
Willing to take up assignments in times of urgent work situations
Job Requirements
Degree/Diploma in Engineering discipline.
Possesses good business acumen.
3 to 5 years of sales experience in engineering discipline preferred.
Candidates in the DataCentre infrastructure/UPS/Cooling/Thermal Management industry will be a key advantage.
